Wing Shack Co – Chatham absolutely blew me away! The food was incredible – the wings were perfectly cooked juicy on the inside and packed with flavor. The variety of sauces is amazing and each one has its own unique kick. The sides were fresh and tasty and everything came piping hot.
The service was just as impressive – friendly quick and attentive making the whole experience even better. You can really tell they care about quality and customer satisfaction.
If you’re craving wings this is hands down the best spot in Chatham. Highly recommend – I’ll definitely be back!
